---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="overflow-x-hidden pt-2">

    <section class="px-6 pt-8 pb-24 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8 mt-2 mb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-brand text-sm mb-4 block">About me</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-7xl">I am Valentina Díaz B. </h1>

      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-900 leading-relaxed">I didn't start my career in a design studio, but in front of
            a compiler. <strong>As a Computer Engineer turned Product Designer,</strong> I approach every project with a
            dual lens: an obsession with high-end visual aesthetics and a deep understanding of technical feasibility.
            This hybrid background allows me to bridge the gap between complex backend logic and seamless, human-centric
            interfaces.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-7 relative h-[400px]">
          <img src="/me-folder.png" alt="About me folder" class="w-3/4 md:w-2/3 mx-auto block h-auto object-cover">
          <span class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-100 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-xl">
            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand mr-2 block"></span>
            Lead Product Designer
          </span>
          <span class="absolute top-2/3 left-8 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-100 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-xl">
            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand mr-2 block"></span>
            Informatics Engineer
          </span>
          <span class="absolute top-4/5 -right-8 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-100 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-xl">
            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand mr-2 block"></span>
            Analog Experience Lover
          </span>
          <span class="absolute top-9/10 left-1/8 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-100 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-xl">
            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-brand mr-2 block"></span>
            Design Systems and Design Ops Specialist
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-24 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">

        <div class="md:col-span-6 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-700">
          <h2
					class="mx-auto mt-2 text-center text-5xl tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">The Technical Rigor behind the Pixel</h2>
          <p>My engineering background defines how I approach design. I don't just aim for visual beauty; I ensure
            products are logically consistent and technically scalable. I have audited extensive Figma libraries and
            migrated multi-brand design systems (Web, iOS, Android) at EPAM for Fortune 500 clients, guaranteeing 100%
            alignment between design and development. I am a firm believer in democratizing design through solid Design
            Ops and clear governance, establishing efficient workflows that boost team velocity without sacrificing
            visual quality.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-6 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-700">
          <h2
					class="mx-auto mt-2 text-center text-5xl tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">A Curated Visual Eye</h2>
          <p>Beyond systems, I possess a passion for premium aesthetics and visual storytelling. This facet is nurtured
            by my exploration of analog photography and creative direction, where organizational rigor meets visual
            curation. I bring this critical eye to every interface, utilizing advanced prototyping and
            micro-interactions (Lottie, motion standards) to elevate the final user experience. I understand a brand not
            as a logo, but as a holistic experience that must be polished and consistent at every digital touchpoint.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-20 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8 border-t border-slate-100 mt-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-8">Technical Stack & Expertise</h3>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 max-w-4xl">
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Figma</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Stakeholder Management</span>

            <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Design
            Systems</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Mentoring</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-brand bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Design
            Ops</span>

          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">AI
            Prompting</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">React</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Tailwind
            CSS</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Astro</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Lottie
            / Motion</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Git</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">Advanced
            Prototyping</span>
          <span
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors cursor-default">OOUX</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>